{"tid":1136495,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長假逼爆　頭等座也遭殃？數十旅客疑搭霸王車","createTime":"2019-05-03T05:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T05:10:24.000Z","uid":225464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fa265f4b94b53a19454b5a59c8ae16c4ed6ae619","tid":1136495,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:02:29.000Z","msg":"長假逼爆 頭等座也遭殃？數十旅客疑搭霸王車<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GXBxrU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GXBxrU&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjNXdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=e7efbfba\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GXBxrU</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190503/photo/bkn-20190503123139702-0503_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190503125849\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190503%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190503123139702-0503_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190503125849&h=ef515a28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知要補飛定博懵？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據Facebook群組「North District 北區」的多張相片可見，星期三（1日）上午的東鐵班次，有不少旅客乘搭頭等車廂，部分人更沒有座位，需全程站立。<br />\n<br />\n惟其後有港鐵職員進行查票工作，發貼者斥謂︰「超過一半人冇補頭等飛，霸佔頭等座位！」逾10名違規的乘客其後需在港鐵九龍塘站落車，由職員跟進情況。<br />\n<br />\n有網民同日亦發文指，有港鐵職員在列車經過上水站後查票，「有成20幾個大陸人冇頭等車票入咗頭等，喺粉嶺站畀人請落車」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190503/photo/bkn-20190503123139702-0503_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190503125849\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190503%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190503123139702-0503_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190503125849&h=5baba6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有多名乘客疑未補頭等車票，被職員帶到客務中心。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"b2dd029c7e8d7ffa36c344d4269a34b40b6edb50","tid":1136495,"uid":48259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:04:14.000Z","msg":"真係好想班狗官呢個星期同班生番迫下"},{"pid":"8ffad2d978c44829e05e1b37ca31e04b29b6ed80","tid":1136495,"uid":22604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T05:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a